  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1653796/" class="title-link">库切的“星空与德律”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1653796"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sogdiana/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1416258-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sogdiana/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">sogdiana</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-02-04"
      class="main-meta">2009-02-04 16:33:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1653796_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《凶年纪事》很好看，不仅在于内容的丰富，还在于结构的精巧，宛如赋格。书的每页都分作三栏，三种声部同时各自发音而又彼此缠绕、相互呼应，以复调形式在文本中、故事里荡展开来，对位谨致，和声恢宏。最上栏又分作两部分——危言与随札，前者是老作家J.C.的政论文字，关于国...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1653796/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1653796_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1653796_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





